values:
"50 Gs? I think she'd prefer 50 jays."
"Yes! That's what we need! Samantha, high as balls, on the inside!"
"I birthed your baby and I beat your bone!"

"I think my wife is a whore, botanist."

"I ate yer egg!"

"How is this the wrong key?"

Ow my very ankle.

Also, hi from Place 11.

I'm listening to We Were Dead Before the Ship Even Sank. This is a good sign for mankind.

Also other good things happened today.
It's 11:09. I wonder if anything will happen at 11:10.

I kind of like Surprise but Continuum is much better.

I made $60 today; $90 technically but I'll end up giving that $30 back anyway.

90% of the time I'm not wrong. Seriously. But 95% of the time I'll claim I am anyway. So I should remind myself once in a while I'm not as wrong as I wanna be.

I'm still not sure I like the scheme of this right now, but I'm still not that concerned with fixing it.
The soles of my feet are killing me. After five days they are still killing me. After six I will have been killed.

"We are ornithologists here. We are not birds."

Also I have an idea that involves being shot in the back and falling over a bannister to one's (not my) death. At some point I may flesh it out.

My legs are very, very red.

My time at Columbia starts Sept. 6th.
Well, that was a resounding failure. Either I'd better do something interesting, or I'd better go around telling people I'm saying things again.

Gonna try this one more time, since I have some time on my hands. My commitment, as always, is suspect, but we'll see how it goes.

At some point, I'll update the color scheme. Maybe. If you've read this message, and you know who I am, please comment - I'm just curious to see if I've still got some existence in me.
